.DT
kneel
Discworld player help
kneel

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
kneel - Change your position to kneeling.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
kneel
kneel on [the] floor
kneel on <object>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Allows you to change your position.  To kneel on the floor, or to kneel on
something, or to just kneel down if you are sitting.
.EP


.SH Examples
.SI 5
> kneel
You kneel down.
> kneel on the floor
You kneel on the floor.
> kneel on table
You kneel on the table.
.EI

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
crouch, lie, meditate, position, sit, stand.
.EP
